Class name: Item
Parent class: None

Responsibilities:
* It's the class storing information about items on our platform.
* When we call a method in Item, we can do the following:
    - getItemName (Return the name of an item)
    - getOwner (Return the owner of an item)
    - getItemPrice (Return the price of an item)
    - getItemQuantity (Return the quantity of an item)
    - changeItemName (change the name of an item)
    - changeItemPrice (change the price of an item)
    - addQuantity (add quantity of an item)
    - subtractQuantity (subtract quantity of an item)
    - toString (Return a string representation of an item)

Collaborators:
- User